name: Solipsist EP
description:
Vocals on Magnetic, Third Eye and Thinner by Pirta Stenius. Guitars by Sami Kaarakainen except for Trigger, guitars by Tuomo Karjalainen. Drums on Linkside by Arttu Stenius. 
Bass, production & various noises by Markku Stenius.

name: Else EP
description:
Guitars and creative synergy by Sami Kaarakainen and Tuomo Karjalainen (Polaroid & Empty Hands solo). Drums on Polaroid, Empty Hands and Out of Pills by Arttu Stenius. 
Special thanks to Juliette for the narration on Polaroid. 
Cover photography by Heidi Korkala. Produced by Markku Stenius.

name: Adrift EP
description:
Guitars and creative synergy by Sami Kaarakainen. Vocals on New Life and En La Oscuridad by Anji Bee. 
Cover photography by Lofihile. 
Produced by Markku Stenius

name: Come EP
description:
Guitars and creative synergy by Sami Kaarakainen. Vocal weirdness on Zero Gravity Container and Dreaming of Wings by Mr Mouse. Guitar on Sixshooter and vocal effects on Dreaming of Wings by Jukka Torso. 
Cover photography by Lofihile. 
Produced by Markku Stenius.
